data.description: Outstanding Re-modeled Home w/ a Designer Flare and New in 2021 a $40,000.00 LG Solar Panel System Including a Generac Energy Storage Component that Functions as a Back Up Generator if the Power is Out~~Save on Electricity, Get Paid Back from the Utility Company, Set it up to Charge Your Electric Car and Have Peace of Mind~~Additional Efficient Features: LED Lighting, Nest Thermostat and Extra Blown-in Insulation~~You'll Love the Renovated Open Kitchen w/ Custom Butcher Block Island, Stylish Refinished Cabinetry, Subway Tile Backsplash, Trendy Fixtures & Quality Stainless Appliances~~Enjoy Hardwood Floors that Flow Throughout the Entry Level~~Perfect for Entertaining the Kitchen is Open to the Large Dining Area Complete w/ a Gas Fireplace & New Hand Crafted Floor to Ceiling Built-in Shelving / Storage~~Gather in the Updated Living Room Boasting Floating Shelving, Wall to Wall Storage Bench and Flat Screen TV Wall Mount System~~Retire to 1 of 3 Bedrooms Including a Large Primary Suite Offering a Private Full Bah and Dual Walk-in Closets~~A Partially Finished Lower Level Presents Many Options with a Rec Room and Space for a Gym~~Beautifully Landscaped Yard, Mature Trees & Multi-Level Decking~~Three Car Garage~~Min to Fenton, Schools, Shopping, Restaurants, Recreation, Golf & US-23~~Hurry~~
